{
  "stem": "8072.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's-- [CLEARS THROAT] And they had-- they had assemblies constantly, you know, because they're picking up prisoners from here to send to this outlying camps to, to work and things like that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was-- in that situation I was fortunate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] Because being-- I was working with this [INAUDIBLE] and the thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So a lot of time when they had assemblies to go out, the barrack-- the in charge of the barracks, he already-- he told them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, leave him alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He doesn't have to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, he's German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He doesn't have to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was able to not to go in the assemblies and was able to stay there for--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It wasn't that great, but at least I, I was alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't-- yeah, I-- I think he was-- didn't, didn't wear the clothes that we had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was more of a different-- they had-- you know, like, we all had the, the signs like the stars.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of them was yellow, some of them was this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and they, they had a badge, also a piece, like, a white pin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's were even a triangle down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Red was political.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Green was murderers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they were murderers and everything like that, but they were in charge of us, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it didn't [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, if they had German people, like we have people now in jail, if they have murderers and things like that, they brought them over to this camp and made them in charge of this.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were given decent food and decent clothing and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The stripes, the, the regular stripes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Star of David, regular stripes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I actually had to wear it even in town before you were liquidated.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
